* Iron looks into the room, smiling but wincing when she sees most of the 
Maximals stop and get hit by beams. But with a flick of her wrist the beams 
shit down and the entire room goes black...to be replaced by a hologram of a 
run down ship with holes in the roof and floor...as if something has broken 
through them.*

" You guys are in the wrong place! You should all be on tennis courts!:

* And with an honest smile she enters the room, the door remaining open for 
Necromancer and Hell Drak if they wanted to come along.*
